"I believe that thanks to our initiative now all inhabitants have a certain link to this building.
Everyone knows your book is part of the library.
Even though he's just there to decorate.
In this way, the MVRDV study has achieved a complete success in that discipline reigns that in the specialized argot is known as "creating an identity".
The city of Spijkenisse has written a piece of the history of literature.
Regardless of how young and unlearned it may be.
Finally, a starting point for conforming to their identity.
