I'm afraid you're gonna keep them alone with this idea, guys.
That's fair.
If some Mexicans are not yet prepared to forgive the United States for the way they treated Mexico a century and a half ago, then they have to accept the fact that some Mexican-Americans are still resented for how they treated their relatives much less time ago.
Hmmm.
